ols, we predict the phase alignment of Planck with a hypothetical\nperfect noiseless CMB experiment, finding decoherence at l > 2900; below this\nvalue Planck can be used most efficiently to constrain non-Gaussianity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2013 19:07:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 16:39:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
