at exchange efficiency. The evolution of the temperature over time, towards\nsteady state, also shows complex behavior: some sites alternately reheat and\ncool down several times, making it difficult to forecast the extracted heat.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2013 11:56:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-05"}
